---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import sampleImg from '../../../../public/images/image1.png';
---
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Image Optimization Demo</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/styles/global.css">
  </head>
  <body class="font-sans bg-slate-50 m-0 p-0">
    <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto mt-12 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-black/5 px-8 py-10 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-blue-500 text-3xl mb-6 font-normal">Image Optimization Demo</h1>
      <div class="text-slate-500 text-lg mb-8">
        This demo shows Astro's built-in image optimization using the <code class="bg-slate-100 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-sm">&lt;Image /&gt;</code> component.
      </div>
      <div class="mb-8">
        <span class="text-blue-500 font-medium mb-2 block">Optimized Image:</span>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-lg px-8 py-6 shadow-sm shadow-black/5 inline-block">
          <Image src={sampleImg} alt="Sample" width={400} class="rounded-lg shadow-sm shadow-black/5" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-8">
        <span class="text-blue-500 font-medium mb-2 block">Unoptimized Image:</span>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-lg px-8 py-6 shadow-sm shadow-black/5 inline-block">
          <img src="/images/image1.png" alt="Sample" width="400" class="rounded-lg shadow-sm shadow-black/5" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
